        "text": "RECORDED 19\nNovember 24, 1950\n62-83894-260\nX-16\nTo:\nDirector of Special Investigations\nThe Inspector General\nDepartment of the Air Force\nThe Pentagon\nWashington, D.C.\nFrom:\nJ. Edgar Hoover, Director, Federal Bureau of Investigation\nSubject: FLYING DISCS"
